OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1783079290
OL,3,CEngland fan spends #40,000 house
OL,4,Cdeposit on World Cup trip with father
OL,6,FAn England fan spent his #40,000 house
OL,7,Fdeposit on taking his father to watch
OL,8,Fthe Three Lions "win the World Cup".
OL,10,FJack Goodwin has pre-booked his
OL,11,Fhotels, flights and tickets to every
OL,12,Fgame England can play in until the
OL,13,Ffinal in New Jersey on July 19.
OL,15,F"We've been to New York, we've seen
OL,16,Fthe World Cup and we're going to see
OL,17,Fus bring it home. It's a simple
OL,18,Fequation," he said.
OL,26,@pD@QOUpD@cO]wD@AOUzD@JO]
