OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1783079290
OL,3,CEngland fan spends #40,000 house
OL,4,Cdeposit on World Cup trip with father
OL,6,FThe 34-year-old, originally from
OL,7,FChichester in West Sussex, said he has
OL,8,Fspent the equivalent of #4,000 on a
OL,9,Fticket to the final, describing the
OL,10,Ftrip as a "once-in-a-lifetime
OL,11,Fopportunity".
OL,13,FJack, who did not give his father's
OL,14,Fname, said: "Me and my dad, we've been
OL,15,Fhere since Dallas.
OL,17,F"We've done Dallas, Boston, New York,
OL,18,Farrived in Atlanta... and we're going
OL,19,Fall the way to the final and we're
OL,20,Fgoing to watch us win the World Cup."
OL,26,@rD@KOUsD@LO]vD@MOUyD@AOU|D@eO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1783079290
OL,3,CEngland fan spends #40,000 house
OL,4,Cdeposit on World Cup trip with father
OL,6,FSpeaking ahead of England's first
OL,7,Fknockout game against the Democratic
OL,8,FRepublic of the Congo in Atlanta, Jack
OL,9,Fsaid: "We're going to smash them 4-0
OL,10,Fand we're going to play Mexico in the
OL,11,FAzteca this Sunday which will be the
OL,12,Fdream game of all games, the creme of
OL,13,Fthe creme."
OL,15,FThe Stoke City fan said he was
OL,16,F"sweating" when Panama held the Three
OL,17,FLions to a 0-0 draw at half-time in
OL,18,Ftheir final group game.
OL,26,@qD@GOUuD@KO]xD@AOUxD@JO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1783079290
OL,3,CEngland fan spends #40,000 house
OL,4,Cdeposit on World Cup trip with father
OL,6,F"We've pre-booked everything now to
OL,7,Fthe final ` hotels, tickets,
OL,8,Feverything sorted.
OL,10,F"We were sweating because we got all
OL,11,Four tickets through the FIFA ballot `
OL,12,Fif we didn't top the group, all of our
OL,13,Ftickets would have become invalid."
OL,15,FJack said his dad's "confidence" meant
OL,16,Fthey booked flights to Atlanta a few
OL,17,Fweeks ago.
OL,19,FHe said: "We booked them a few weeks
OL,20,Fago, so we were pretty confident.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUuD@cO]wD@UOUwD@`O]{D@JOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1783079290
OL,3,CEngland fan spends #40,000 house
OL,4,Cdeposit on World Cup trip with father
OL,6,F"I mean, my dad was pretty confident,
OL,7,Fso I went with his confidence."
OL,9,FExplaining how he had funded the trip,
OL,10,FMr Goodwin said his tickets were all
OL,11,Fat face value, but were still "mega
OL,12,Fexpensive".
OL,14,F"It's been very expensive. I saved up
OL,15,Ffor a house and I blew my whole house
OL,16,Fdeposit taking me and my dad out," he
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,19,FQuestioned on how much he had spent,
OL,20,Fhe continued: "How long's a piece of
OL,21,Fstring? A good #40,000.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@_O]sD@_OUtD@JO]vD@AOUxD@bO]|D@
OL,26,AOOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
