OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1783079290
OL,3,CEngland fan spends #40,000 house
OL,4,Cdeposit on World Cup trip with father
OL,6,F"We've got everything face value but
OL,7,Fthat's not to say it was cheap ` it
OL,8,Fwas mega expensive still."
OL,10,FHe added: "Well, I've got no kids,
OL,11,FI've got no wife, so why not?
OL,13,F"This is a once-in-a-lifetime
OL,14,Fopportunity."
OL,16,FJack described the cost of World Cup
OL,17,Ffinal tickets as a "joke".
OL,19,FHe said: "For the group games... I
OL,20,Fthink it was around 350 dollars. We
OL,21,Fwere in the Gods.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@ZO]rD@KOUuD@AOUvD@MO]yD@TOUyD@
OL,26,AYO]{D@JOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
