OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1783079290
OL,3,CEngland fan spends #40,000 house
OL,4,Cdeposit on World Cup trip with father
OL,6,F"But we've got category one tickets
OL,7,Fnow for the next few games, and they
OL,8,Fwere 600 dollars face value.
OL,10,F"The ticket for the final, which is a
OL,11,Fjoke, was through the England
OL,12,FSupporters Club.
OL,14,F"Face value for category two was 8,000
OL,15,FAustralian dollars, so about #4,000."
OL,17,FHe added: "We've met a lot of people
OL,18,Fthat did ballots and didn't get
OL,19,Ftickets so we're extremely lucky to be
OL,20,Fhere to be honest."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUvD@AOUwD@eO]yD@KOU|D@SO]
